SUMMARY:Live Music and Food Truck at Great Bear Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Live Music & Food Truck Night at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis \nFriday\, May 1 | 5–8pmTicket Includes: Glass of Wine & Live Music\nKick off your weekend with smooth jazz\, incredible tacos\, and vineyard vibes at Great Bear! \n The Potential Jazz Ensemble will be setting the tone from 6–7:30pm with a vibrant\, soulful performance. This talented group blends classic jazz roots with fresh\, creative energy—featuring saxophone\, bass\, guitar\, piano\, and drums for a rich\, dynamic sound you won’t want to miss.\n Come hungry! Maiz Mexican Food will be onsite from 5–8pm\, serving up authentic\, family-made Mexican favorites—from tacos and quesadillas to huaraches\, all packed with bold flavor and signature smoked meats.\nYour ticket includes a glass of wine\, with more available by the glass or bottle as you relax\, sip\, and soak in the sounds of the evening.\n Food Truck: 5–8pm Live Music: 6–7:30pm\nGreat music\, delicious food\, and a beautiful vineyard setting—the perfect recipe for a Friday night. Grab your friends and join us!
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/live-music-and-food-truck-at-great-bear-vineyards-3/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
